{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-delicatto-rastreio",
    "name": "Delicatto — Rastreio + Admin",
    "description": "## Backend Delicatto — consulta pública de rastreio\n\n**POST** `{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/consultar` — corpo JSON `{ \"codigo\": \"...\" }` (sem token no cliente).\n\n### curl — local (`npm start`)\n```bash\ncurl -sS -X POST \"http://localhost:3000/api/rastreio/consultar\" \\\\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json\" \\\\\n  -d '{\"codigo\":\"SEU_CODIGO\"}'\n```\n```bash\ncurl -sS \"http://localhost:3000/api/rastreio/health\"\n```\n\n### curl — produção (Render)\n```bash\ncurl -sS -X POST \"https://formulariodelicatto.onrender.com/api/rastreio/consultar\" \\\\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json\" \\\\\n  -d '{\"codigo\":\"SEU_CODIGO\"}'\n```\nNo Postman: **Import → Raw text** e cole um dos comandos acima (ajuste o código).\n\n---\n\n## Melhor Envio (API externa)\n\nAutenticação ME: **JWT do painel** em `{{me_panel_access_token}}`.\n\n`GET {{me_base}}/api/v2/me/orders/search?q={{codigoRastreio}}` — parâmetro **`?q=`**.\n\nImporte `Delicatto-local.postman_environment.json` e preencha `baseUrl`, `me_panel_access_token`, `me_base`, `codigoRastreio`.\n\n**Admin** e outros pedidos extra continuam desativados; reative no Postman se precisar.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "description": "Backend Node (local ou https://formulariodelicatto.onrender.com)" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "codigoRastreio", "value": "" },
    { "key": "envioId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "me_base", "value": "https://www.melhorenvio.com.br" },
    { "key": "me_panel_access_token", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Backend — API pública",
      "description": "Usa `baseUrl` (localhost ou URL do Render). Equivalente curl na descrição da coleção.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health rastreio",
          "description": "```bash\ncurl -sS \"{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/health\"\n```",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Consultar envio (público)",
          "description": "```bash\ncurl -sS -X POST \"{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/consultar\" \\\\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json\" \\\\\n  -d '{\"codigo\":\"{{codigoRastreio}}\"}'\n```",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"codigo\": \"{{codigoRastreio}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/consultar"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin (desativado)",
      "description": "Reative os itens no Postman se for usar rotas admin.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar envios",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/envios"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar cliente",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"Cliente teste\",\n  \"email\": \"teste@example.com\",\n  \"telefone\": \"11999999999\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/clientes"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar pedido",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"codigo\": \"PED-001\",\n  \"titulo\": \"Pedido teste\",\n  \"clienteId\": null\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/pedidos"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cadastrar envio",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"codigoRastreio\": \"{{codigoRastreio}}\",\n  \"melhorEnvioShipmentId\": null,\n  \"pedidoId\": null\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/envios"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sincronizar envio por ID",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/envios/{{envioId}}/sincronizar"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sincronizar todos",
          "disabled": true,
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Rastreio-Admin-Token", "value": "{{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rastreio/admin/sincronizar-todos"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Melhor Envio (API externa)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Pesquisar pedidos — orders/search (ME_PANEL_ACCESS_TOKEN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{me_panel_access_token}}" },
              { "key": "User-Agent", "value": "Delicatto Postman (seu-email@exemplo.com)" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{me_base}}/api/v2/me/orders/search?q={{codigoRastreio}}",
              "host": ["{{me_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v2", "me", "orders", "search"],
              "query": [{ "key": "q", "value": "{{codigoRastreio}}" }]
            },
            "description": "GET com query `q` (não use `/search/q=`). Token = JWT Permissões de acesso no painel ME. Sem Cookie do browser."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
